{"tid":984693,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【10年挑戰】尼馬瘦到似飢民 麥巴比仲係細路哥","createTime":"2019-01-17T04:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T08:40:40.000Z","uid":199590,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"e893e79dd6956b82639c13867c02c578ef4bc09a","tid":984693,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D3EjV4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD3EjV4d.jpg&h=3ed58a1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JW7mpXz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJW7mpXz.jpg&h=4b6b4781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzsaihA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzsaihA.jpg&h=7a231bae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1tMA4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1tMA4g.jpg&h=aeaf8e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAFCHKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAFCHKh.jpg&h=7f8b11cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xuecwCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxuecwCD.jpg&h=0cc95029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krLrA4j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrLrA4j.jpg&h=9c5a99a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHoHTQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHoHTQ4.jpg&h=41febd12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8caihL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8caihL.jpg&h=667b7395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1GWeKXO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1GWeKXO.jpg&h=9594c068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHbm9pu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHbm9pu.jpg&h=06a04cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社交媒體近日掀起「#10 years challenge」熱潮，不少網民將自己的樣子，作前後10年的對照。不少外國媒體，都將現時世界各大球星來個當年今日比較，包括基斯坦奴朗拿度、美斯、尼馬、保羅普巴及基利安麥巴比等，都已模樣大不同。<br />\n<br />\n2009年，美斯與C朗已在世界球壇開始佔據球王之位，而當年只得21歲的美斯，年尾捧得金球獎及世界足球先生，雙喜臨門，翻看他10年前的照片，仍然非常青澀，也不像現在般鬍鬚滿面；前1年助曼聯奪得英超及歐聯雙冠王的C朗，事實上外觀分別不大，仍是一樣有型。<br />\n<br />\n反而，尼馬及基利安麥巴比兩位PSG球星，當年一個在山度士初出茅廬才16歲，另一個更只得10歲，房內仍掛著C朗的海報，樣子有很大出入，其中尼馬瘦到像沒有吃飯多日的飢民一樣。至於喜愛變髮的普巴，當年仍在曼聯青年軍效力，但髮型已經算「潮」，很明顯電過，只是比起現時的他，當然有所不及。<br />\n<br />\n回看10年前的英超，仍處Big 4時代，曼城及熱刺未入流，而那一季由費格遜爵士仍在領隊之位、有基斯坦奴朗拿度及朗尼等壓陣的曼聯，奪得聯賽冠軍，但當年一隊陣容中的球員，已沒有一人留隊。"},{"pid":"ba311443ac11e666539d03e17c1bbd1e2781a2cd","tid":984693,"uid":693,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GjOKM1C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGjOKM1C.jpg&h=c85d2564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nmbappe &amp; c7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a31b13d348f5513feba3ac0b9d9f300c55c902","tid":984693,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:15:01.000Z","msg":"鬼佬大得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfe8e887a1be455ee8f505ea2aa63c7d5998d4a","tid":984693,"uid":18669,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"點解尼馬個樣變得咁勁"},{"pid":"e8bfc677f902d24d1a1ff0b56792802df42851e4","tid":984693,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:16:35.000Z","msg":"高普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdf6787d743307c0f4042bb41db80f5f77c64eb","tid":984693,"uid":30808,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:16:59.000Z","msg":"咸爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9a7a41ac25a9e